               <p>On last Saturday about four o'clock, while I was walking in <placeName id="t17801206-31-crimeloc165">Gracechurch-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17801206-31-crimeloc165" type="placeName" value="Gracechurch-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17801206-31-crimeloc165" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17801206-31-off163 t17801206-31-crimeloc165"></join>, I observed the prisoner walked on my left side; he went round to my right and picked my handkerchief out of my pocket. I immediately seised him, and he dropped the handkerchief; I went to pick it up and he ran away. I pursued him and cried stop thief! he was not out of my sight till he was taken.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17801206-31-person348">
                  JOHN
                   GODFREY
               <interp inst="t17801206-31-person348" type="surname" value="GODFREY"></interp>
